# Copy this file to .dev.vars and fill in the values.
# .dev.vars is loaded by `wrangler dev` and overrides wrangler.jsonc vars locally.
# Never commit .dev.vars — it is gitignored.

# Email OTPs are sent via the TALASH_EMAIL send_email binding — no key needed here.
# SMS OTPs are currently logged to console (provider not yet configured).
